<mvc:View 
    controllerName="UI5_course.controller.Task3" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:ux3="sap.ui.ux3" id="shell">
    <ux3:Shell id="idShellView" appTitle="{i18n>Task3.title}" worksetItemSelected="onNavigate" showTools="true">
        <ux3:headerItems>
            <Button id="bnBack3" 
                    class="nav_back" 
                    icon="sap-icon://navigation-left-arrow" 
                    text="{i18n>btnBackText}" 
                    type="Emphasized" 
                    press="onNavBack"/>
        </ux3:headerItems>
        <ux3:worksetItems>
            <ux3:NavigationItem text="{i18n>subView1}" key="key1" />
            <ux3:NavigationItem text="{i18n>subView2}" key="key2" />
        </ux3:worksetItems>
        <ux3:content>
            <mvc:XMLView viewName="UI5_course.view.Customers" />
        </ux3:content>
    </ux3:Shell>
</mvc:View>